343
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:47,239
So they will investigate.

344
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,719
But they won't find any evidence.

345
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:50,460
In the end, the case will go cold.

346
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:53,039
Because you and I, the only people

347
