You must have countless ways

351
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:09,110
to make me disappear without a trace.

352
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:11,349
Why are you choosing to go down

353
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,740
and die with me?

354
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,630
Revenge.

355
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:17,310
Revenge?

356
00:19:23,190 --> 00:19:24,959
You were the one who almost killed me.

357
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:26,500
If anyone's getting revenge,

358
00:19:26,630 --> 00:19:28,759
it should be me.

359
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:33,910
Do you know what it's like
to watch someone you love die

360
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,670
because of you?

361
