I do.

362
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,180
If you had died in that last job,

363
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:51,910
I would've gotten my payment

364
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:54,110
and saved my mom.

365
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,189
But you didn't die.

366
00:19:56,190 --> 00:19:58,150
Why didn't you die?

367
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:01,020
I've done this for a long time.

368
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:03,350
And this is the only time I missed.

369
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:05,189
The one job to kill you,

370
00:20:05,190 --> 00:20:06,389
