371
00:20:06,390 --> 00:20:08,020
You didn't die.

372
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:10,999
But my mom died.

373
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,279
By the time I rushed back,

374
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:14,310
I saw her take her last breath.

375
00:20:14,320 --> 00:20:16,460
How could I not hate you?

376
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:18,870
Split up and search.

377
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:33,959
Watching the person you love die
in front of you.

378
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,389
I was completely helpless.

379
00:20:35,390 --> 00:20:37,110
I was helpless.

380
00:20:39,190 --> 00:20:42,039
You know what that feels like too,

381
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:43,150
don't you? Ning Jing!

382
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:44,669
Ning Jing!

383
00:20:44,670 --> 00:20:47,110
What do you think
that partner of yours was thinking

384
00:20:48,910 --> 00:20:50,149
before she died?

385
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:51,310
Shut up.

386
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:56,070
Do you know
what it feels like to burn alive?

387
00:20:56,190 --> 00:20:57,700
I said shut up.

388
00:20:59,670 --> 00:21:01,540
Ning Jing cared about you so much.

389
00:21:01,910 --> 00:21:03,039
And what did you do?

390
00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:06,500
In the end, you let her burn alive.

391
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:08,589
Do you know
what it's like to be burned alive?

392
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:10,799
The nervous system gets destroyed,

393
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:11,909
you suffocate, lose oxygen,

394
00:21:11,910 --> 00:21:14,740
and instinctively start flailing.

395
00:21:21,670 --> 00:21:24,460
But by then,
your skin is already burned.

396
00:21:24,560 --> 00:21:27,350
The pain is so intense
that the body goes into shock.

397
00:21:32,590 --> 00:21:36,070
But the intense pain wakes you up.

398
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:45,020
Then comes the instinct to scratch
at the burning flesh.

399
00:21:49,630 --> 00:21:52,429
Do you know
what's burning at that point?

400
00:21:52,430 --> 00:21:54,780
The fat under the skin.

401
00:21:55,150 --> 00:21:56,180
Like roasting meat.

402
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,109
Roasted meat.

403
00:21:58,110 --> 00:22:00,759
- Stop it. I said stop!
- That's what it is, roasted meat.

404
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:02,039
Stop it already!

405
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:04,669
Shut it! Just shut it!

406
00:22:04,670 --> 00:22:08,780
Help! Roasted meat! It's BBQ!

407
00:22:27,630 --> 00:22:29,909
You don't deserve to live in this world.

408
00:22:29,910 --> 00:22:32,519
I'm not worthy of living
in this world too.

409
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:34,430
I'm serious.

410
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:36,940
Come.

411
00:22:38,830 --> 00:22:39,980
Come,

412
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:41,630
